text: Norimasa Iwai (born 12 March 1973) is a Japanese gymnast. He competed in five events at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Japan Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Nagano Prefecture Category:People from Matsumoto, Nagano
